寫左個bot <a href="https://lih.kg/1660642" target="_blank">https://lih.kg/1660642</a><br />
<br />
如果想用樓主既script交稅，要加幾行code，因為段script無揀到帳單類別<br />
<br />
首先搵左呢行code先：<br />
<pre><code data-type="">confirmSubmit(); </code></pre><br />
然後係呢行<strong>上面</strong>加以下既code<br />
<pre><code data-type="">var billTypeSelect = document.querySelector('select[name=&quot;BILLTYPE&quot;]');
billTypeSelect.value = '01';
var evt = document.createEvent('HTMLEvents');
evt.initEvent('change', false, true);
billTypeSelect.dispatchEvent(evt);</code></pre>

